      "title": "[v12] Parquet-\u003eCSV (kmon)",
      "text": "%spark_high.pyspark\nS3_PATH_PARQ \u003d \"s3a://bigdata/kmon/parquet\"\nS3_PATH_CSV  \u003d \"s3a://bigdata/kmon/csv\"\nparq_df \u003d spark.read.parquet(S3_PATH_PARQ)\nprint(\"Parquet 파티션: \" + str(parq_df.rdd.getNumPartitions()))\nparq_df.write.mode(\"overwrite\").option(\"header\",\"true\").option(\"encoding\",\"UTF-8\").option(\"compression\",\"gzip\").csv(S3_PATH_CSV)\nprint(\"CSV 완료 -\u003e \" + S3_PATH_CSV)\n",
